headline: Uber CFO to Participate in Fireside Chat Hosted by Barclays
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, November 26, 2024--Uber Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: UBER) today announced that Prashanth Mahendra-Rajah, CFO, will participate in a fireside chat at the Barclays 22nd Annual Global Technology Conference on Wednesday, December 11. Mr. Mahendra-Rajah is scheduled to appear at 1:20pm PT (4:20pm ET).
